        <heading>3175.  Applicability of general rules of pledge</heading>
        <content>
          <p>Art. 3175.  Applicability of general rules of pledge
In all matters for which no special provision is made in this Chapter, the pledge of
the lessor's rights in the lease of an immovable and its rents is governed by the provisions of
Chapter 1 of this Title.</p>
        </content>
